Want to talk about blessed? My plan was to give the kids a few very small presents and some stocking stuffers. 90% of these are from customers who became friends and friends who became family. #christmasspirit #christmasisbetterwithkids #blessedandgrateful
The kids got spaceships for Christmas. Where do I find these for adults? 🤣 #crashaddict #bumperbuddy #madetocrash
Bumper cars were a hit!

I can guarantee, with 100% certainty, I would not be who I am today without the influence of this legend who was taken too soon. From rocking DC shoes as a punk kid in school to terrorizing the town and back roads in my STI. A lot of my skills and style came from attempting to mimic Ken’s. My friends and I would pile in my STI and “gymkhana” every parking lot we could find. Every form of motorsports and marketing has been influenced by him. Of all his accomplishments I’m sure he was most proud of his family. Thanks for being such a badass and always pushing the limits of what can be done physically and visually! If you see my pops, tell him I said hi and help him give heaven a little hell. #kenblock #gonetoosoon #legendsneverdie

The truth 99% of the time. Invest in a machine and in a year or two it is out of date. Invest in yourself and that skill will be with you your entire career through every machine. #poynterspointers #masteroffaster #pianolessonsbeforethegrandpiano

Three years! The best three years of my life. Even though your mother hates you growing up it is absolutely my favorite thing. I love watching you take on and conquer new challenges. I love watching you be a mini mama to your little brothers. I love watching you be so strong and confident already. Most of all I love that god allowed me to be your father. I know I didn’t deserve it but your mother and I will work everyday to give you the best chance at a happy and successful life.
